The optimum regimen of maintenance treatment after first-line chemotherapy in patients with metastatic colorectal cancer (mCRC) is unknown.

 This study was designed to determine the efficacy and safety of maintenance treatment with capecitabine metronomic chemotherapy versus conventional chemotherapy.

